FT  02 JUN 93 / World Commodities Prices: Cotton
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
No spot or shipment sales were recorded in Liverpool during the week ended
28 May, against 196 tonnes in the previous week. Activity was severely
restrained and business was on narrow lines. High cost of raw cotton
deterred users from increasing their purchases.
