</XX>
<CO>Hanix Industry.
    Tokyo Electric Power.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>JPZ  Japan, Asia.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P3531 Construction Machinery.
